Join us at the South Coast MA Guitar Show & Swap Meet on March 24, 2019 !

We welcome all guitarists, musicians, vendors, collectors, and other interested individuals to our South Coast MA Guitar Show & Swap Meet - the perfect venue to buy, sell, or swap guitars, amps, and all kinds of musical equipment & gear !

General Information

  • When:   Sunday, March 24, 2019 from 10:00 am - 3:00 pm
  • Where:   UMass Dartmouth, Woodland Commons, 285 Old Westport Road, North Dartmouth, MA 02747 - Directions
    Note: Please use Parking Lot #5 !     - (Parking Lots 7 & 8 are under construction)
  • General Admission:   $10. / Children 12 & under FREE
  • Vendor Table Pricing:   Each table is $100. Additional tables are $50. each - Vendor Information   |   Payment Information
  • Visit Our Facebook Site: facebook.com/SouthcoastGuitarShow


Download: 2019 South Coast MA Guitar Show Flyer - (Pictured below)


Join us at our 2019 Concert Series! - (Marion MA Music Hall)

  • April 7, 2019 - Marcus Monteiro
  • May 19, 2019 - October Road / A Tribute to James Taylor
  • June 2, 2019 - Jim Robitaille Trio
  • July 28, 2019 - Steve Katz of Blood, Sweat, and Tears fame
  • August 18, 2019 - Danielle M and the Glory Junkies
  • September 29, 2019 - Giocosa Quartet
  • October 20, 2019 - 440 Gypsy Jazz
  • November 17, 2019 Musicians and Their Visual Artwork Featuring: Peter Stone, Butch McCarthy, and Ken Richards.

Tickets:   $20 General Admission;   $15 Seniors/Students;   $10 Second Half Members
